.0075, 171.727, 170.7289, 170.0916, 170.0132, 169.7806, 170.2379, 169.4339, 170.6627, 170.8079, 169.8762, 170.1703, 170.8218, 170.2802, 170.3788, 170.0526, 170.4937, 170.2217, 169.7129, 169.3107, 169.3493, 168.2725, 168.5295, 168.4291, 168.8611, 169.5032, 170.0937, 171.0482, 170.6666, 170.0812, 171.8042, 173.1488, 173.6492, 174.5045, 174.1359, 174.4576, 174.5117, 175.3355, 174.5103, 174.6047, 174.9367, 175.562, 174.7246, 174.7501, 173.8682, 174.4984, 176.2967, 177.2084, 176.3053, 175.85, 178.4136, 177.3609, 177.3431, 177.4521, 179.1688, 178.9421, 179.437, 179.587, 179.8201, 180.0603, 180.9446, 181.7023, 182.5266, 182.6952, 181.9625, 182.4456, 182.6472, 181.9978, 182.6047, 183.1114, 183.6268, 183.0934, 183.3747, 184.1723, 183.1838, 182.8256, 183.2623, 183.4129, 184.9243, 185.3111, 185.7328, 187.2167, 186.4929, 187.634, 186.7717, 187.9944, 188.0861, 187.8856, 188.5819, 188.4565, 188.795, 187.7913, 189.0926, 188.0886, 188.0728, 187.882, 187.9936, 187.316, 186.556, 186.2686, 186.8551, 187.5408, 187.5634, 188.1743, 187.6426, 189.1856, 188.7433, 188.6034, 188.0257, 187.8546, 189.9497, 190.3581, 190.4076, 189.9808, 188.7735, 188.5329, 187.9969, 187.7031, 188.1007, 188.9303, 188.7885, 190.7682, 191.5836, 191.8887, 191.9795, 190.9249, 191.1882, 193.6694, 194.3992, 195.9199, 197.9394, 198.4307, 197.2633, 197.8672, 198.7244, 196.3432, 191.9978, 192.0906, 193.5859, 192.9229, 193.4588, 193.4381, 194.0308, 195.1521, 193.5632, 196.0737, 197.2224, 196.5634, 196.6816, 197.1318, 196.5658, 196.1294, 196.4498, 196.3369, 194.0545, 191.4311, 196.603, 191.1754, 188.9131, 190.3217, 190.4014, 189.8998, 190.0625, 192.1167, 189.2026, 189.5224, 189.3206], "summary_html": "<h1>商品基本面因子探索之甲醇 — 库存z-score反转因子</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报梳理了甲醇产业链基本面因子（供应/需求/库存/价差四大类），发现生产利润和库存对价格有显著的约束作用。核心交易逻辑是：计算基本面因子的滚动z-score，当z-score偏离到极端水平时反向开仓（均值回归），z-score回归正常后平仓。将此逻辑推广到全品种商品期货，库存因子（inventory_21）表现最优，因为库存极端偏高的品种往往面临供应过剩压力导致价格下跌，反之库存极低则供需紧张支撑价格上涨。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.03</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-8.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.3</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.71</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.18 / 1.41</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.33</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.87</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.18</span></td><td>1.45</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.05</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.1</span></td><td>0.56</td><td>1.61</td><td>1.7</td><td>0.91</td><td>0.9</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.32</span></td><td>1.2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>52.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>24.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>库存z-score信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_t^i = \\frac{I_t^i - \\bar{I}_{t-W:t}^i}{\\sigma_{I_{t-W:t}}^i}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">I_t^i</span> 为品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 日的库存（inventory_21），<span class=\"math-tex\">W=200</span> 为滚动窗口。</p>\n<p>持仓信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_t^i = \\begin{cases} -1 &amp; \\text{if } z_t^i &gt; \\theta \\text{ (库存极高→做空)} \\\\ +1 &amp; \\text{if } z_t^i &lt; -\\theta \\text{ (库存极低→做多)} \\\\ \\text{前值} &amp; \\text{otherwise (持仓不变)} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p>当 <span class=\"math-tex\">|z_t^i| &lt; \\theta/2</span> 时平仓（z-score回归中性）。<span class=\"math-tex\">\\theta=1.0</span> 为入场阈值。</p>\n<p>仓位经过 vol_target_scale（目标年化波动率15%）缩放后输出。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>10个变体，inv_zscore_raw Sharpe 1.10最优；TS IC=0.023，信号有效</td><td>初始实现全部因子：时序z-score反转(利润/库存) + 截面排名(利润/库存/基差/ry) + 综合组合</td><td>Sharpe 1.10，所有gate通过</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>对库存z-score取反后传入helper导致信号方向翻转</td><td>错误：pre-negate z-score后reversal helper双重取反，27个库存变体全部负Sharpe</td><td>Sharpe降至0.73 (basis_rank)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>R3</strong></td><td>修复信号方向，保持helper内部方向判断 + 参数网格(3 window x 3 threshold x 3 hold) + IC gate</td><td>修复reversal方向，添加27个参数组合 + 2个IC gate变体</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.31</strong>，14个变体&gt;0.8，决策skip</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R2 的信号方向错误暴露了 z-score reversal 中方向处理的微妙性——库存作为负向因子，必须在 helper 内部处理方向（高z→做空），而非预先取反后调用通用 reversal。R3 修正后 Sharpe 从 0.73 提升到 1.31。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（59个品种有效），最佳盈利品种：CF、FG、RB、SI、AP</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 中长期（z-score极端到回归需数周至数月），hold_days=10</li>\n<li><strong>数据依赖</strong>: inventory_21字段（库存21日口径），非空率~54%，部分品种/日期无数据</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 研报原文针对甲醇单品种，推广到全品种后利润因子效果弱（profit Sharpe仅0.24）\n<p>- 截面IC偏低（0.01），策略主要依赖时序信号而非截面排序 - 2018年yearly Sharpe接近0，该年基本面因子整体失效</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>EXIT_THR</code></td><td><code>0.5</code></td><td>ENTRY_THR / 2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.17s</li>\n</ul>"}